• Architecture → Build in a clean-room environment (design before action)

• Workflow → Educate → Build → Challenge → Decide

• Teaching Edition → Expand the system for learning and training

🔹 Core Principle:
AI assists thinking. Human intelligence determines truth.

🔹 Critical Safety:
AI chat logs are not protected or confidential.

Do not upload protected discovery, privileged communications, or confidential records.

This is not about replacing judgment.

It’s about strengthening it.

Record before remedy.

Method before conclusion.

If you're building, litigating, or thinking through complex problems—structure matters.

